318
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:00,700
Naquela época

319
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:04,600
a largura de banda da Internet na conexão transatlântica

320
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:05,400
era muito limitada

321
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,400
